<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 1991, <it>Research Methods in Social Network Analysis</it>. with Linton C. Freeman and A. Kimball Romney. Transaction Publishers. </entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 1998, <it>Kinship, Networks, and Exchange : Structural Analysis in the Social Sciences</it>, with Thomas Schweizer. Cambridge University Press.</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 2004, <it>Network Analysis and Ethnographic Problems: Process Models of a Turkish Nomad Clan</it>. with Ulla Johansen and <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://eclectic.ss.uci.edu/~drwhite/turks/Fwd.pdf">
